I suspect you want something like
```suggestion
first_by_subject = {}
for msg in public_response['messages']:
    if hashPR.search(msg['subject']) and msg['display_recipient'] == 'PR reviews' and msg['subject'] not in first_by_subject:
        first_by_subject[msg['subject']] = msg['id']
```
and then `first_by_subject` contains _every_ thread with the PR number in its title, in case there was more than one.
